y    am eastern standard time san jose califbusiness wirenutanix the webscale converged infrastructure company today announced the appointment of sunil potti to the position of senior vice president of engineering and product management with more than  years of datacenter and networking experience sunil joins nutanix from citrix nasdaqctxs where he led the citrix netscaler business for over five years of record growth throughout his career he has built industryleading products and scaled teams against intense competition from large incumbent players at nutanix he will oversee all product functions including product strategy development and quality “sunil is an entrepreneur at heart who has both built and scaled successful enterprise businesses” said dheeraj pandey cofounder and ceo nutanix “the coming five years of nutanix require people like sunil who bring together the ‘why’ of product management with the ‘how’ and ‘what’ of engineering he is a worldclass product executive who is broad and customercentric i am delighted he is here to build on our act ii” overseeing citrix’s netscaler business sunil was responsible for record growth over five consecutive years and cementing netscaler as a respected datacenter infrastructure solution powering many of the world’s largest clouds internet properties global enterprises and service providers he joined citrix from f networks where he was vice president of the acceleration and virtualization group prior to f he cofounded and led all product efforts for applicationoriented networking at cisco previous to this sunil was an early employee at synchrony a crm startup acquired by divine where he headed products and engineering sunil holds a master’s degree in computer science from pennsylvania state university “nutanix is upending the market by providing truly innovative webscale technology to enterprises and global service providers” said sunil potti “i have always been passionate about working on fast growing and innovative technologies and nutanix has the most impressive combination of market transformation opportunity disruptive technology and world class talent i have seen in a relatively short period of time nutanix has built strong brand equity and inspired delight with over  customers worldwide by being the only solution to make datacenter infrastructure truly simple to be joining the company at this stage is very exciting” about nutanix nutanix delivers webscale converged infrastructure to medium and large enterprises with its softwaredriven virtual computing platform natively converging compute and storage into a single solution to drive unprecedented simplicity in the datacenter customers can start with a few servers and scale to thousands with predictable performance and economics with a proprietary elastic data fabric and consumergrade management nutanix is the blueprint for applicationoptimized and policydriven infrastructure learn more at wwwnutanixcom or follow up on twitter nutanix contacts liberty communications for nutanixscott beaver nutanixlibertycommscomornutanixdeclan waters director corporate communicationsdeclannutanixcom contacts liberty communications for nutanixscott beaver nutanixlibertycommscomornutanixdeclan waters director corporate communicationsdeclannutanixcom search advanced news search advanced news search log in sign up sunil potti executive profile  biography  bloomberg july    am et internet software and services company overview of nutanix inc snapshotpeople  overviewboard memberscommittees executive profile sunil potti chief product and development officer nutanix incagetotal calculated compensationthis person is connected to  board members in  different organizations across  different industriesas of fiscal year  background mr sunil potti has been the chief product  development officer at nutanix inc since february   and served as its senior vice president of engineering and product management from january  to february   with more than  years of d