th sketch press releasesnutanix appoints sunil potti a  january nutanix appoints sunil potti as senior vice president of engineering and product management former citrix vp and gm brings broad portfolio of product engineering and general management experience san jose calif  january   – nutanix the webscale converged infrastructure company today announced the appointment of sunil potti to the position of senior vice president of engineering and product management with more than  years of experience in the datacenter and networking industries sunil joins nutanix from citrix nasdaq ctxs where he led the citrix netscaler business for over five years of record growth throughout his career he has built industryleading products and scaled teams against intense competition from large incumbent players at nutanix he will oversee all product functions including product strategy development and quality “sunil is a respected data center luminary that brings a history of proven success” said dheeraj pandey cofounder and ceo nutanix “overseeing citrix’s netscaler business he was responsible for record growth over five consecutive years and cementing netscaler as a respected data center infrastructure solution powering many of the world’s largest clouds internet properties global enterprises and service providers sunil’s extensive experience with rapidly growing companies fits well with nutanix’s status as the fastest growing enterprise infrastructure company of the past decade and we are delighted that he has chosen to join our team” sunil joined citrix from f networks where he was vice president of the acceleration and virtualization group prior to f he cofounded and led all product efforts for applicationoriented networking at cisco previous to this sunil was an early employee at synchrony a crm startup acquired by divine where he headed products and engineering sunil holds a master’s degree in computer science from pennsylvania state university “nutanix is upending the market by providing truly innovative webscale technology to enterprises and global service providers” said sunil potti “i have always been passionate about working on fast growing and innovative technologies and nutanix has the most impressive combination of technology and talent i have seen to be joining the company at this stage is truly exciting”  about nutanix nutanix delivers webscale converged infrastructure to medium and large enterprises with its softwaredriven virtual computing platform natively converging compute and storage into a single solution to drive unprecedented simplicity in the datacenter customers can start with a few servers and scale to thousands with predictable performance and economics with a proprietary elastic data fabric and consumergrade management nutanix is the blueprint for applicationoptimized and policydriven infrastructure learn more at wwwnutanixcom or follow up on twitter nutanix   resources enterprise cloud for dummies take a test drive gartner magic quadrant for integrated systems previous postnext post this site uses cookies to enhance your experience ok learn more what we do what is hyperconverged infrastructure back solutions key solutions enterprise applicationsvdivirtualization  clouddata protectionremote  branch officeexplore all solutions back featured workloads citrix xenapp  xendesktopsap business suitemicrosoft sql serveroracle dbsplunkexplore all workloads back industry solutions educationfinancial serviceshealthcarestate  local governmentfederal governmentexplore all industries back back products enterprise cloud platform products overviewacropolis infrastructure stackprism managementcalm app automationxi cloud servicesnutanix xpresscommunity editiontools and technologies back product specifications hardware platformssoftware options back back support  services support product supportsupport phone numbers back services consulting servicestraining  certification back back partners partner network technology alliancessyste